g aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104amz1665702708928.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/amz1665702708928.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/amz1665702708928.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"amz1665702708928\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Global ProcScript\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"amz1665702708928__global_procscript_315259\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Global ProcScript is a Development Object that defines a ProcScript function that is\n      linked into components at runtime when called by ProcScript in the component. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"amz1665702708928__p_d96038e1_d96039e1_d96040e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cvq1665702579531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cvq1665702579531.html\" title=\"Global ProcScripts are global objects that are located in a runtime library and can be called from any ProcScript in the application. They enable you to define common functionality for use by one or more applications.\">Global ProcScripts</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"amz1665702708928__topic_d64132e1_d64133e1_d64134e1_d64135e1_d64136e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d346707e63\">\n                     \n Characteristics\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">prc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wcl1665702709004.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcl1665702709004.html\" title=\"A Global ProcScript Library contains Global ProcScript objects, which are linked into components at runtime when called from other ProcScript in the application.\">Global ProcScript Library</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcName</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>.prc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"amz1665702708928__table_d10649e1_d10650e1_d10651e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">libprc:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LibraryName</var>/prc:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScriptName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"amz1665702708928__topic_d64137e1_d64138e1_d64139e1_d64140e1_d64141e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d346707e269\">\n                     \n Properties\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"amz1665702708928__p_d96047e1_d96048e1_d96049e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38858e1_d38859e1_d38860e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38861e1_d38862e1_d38863e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38864e1_d38865e1_d38866e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38867e1_d38868e1_d38869e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38870e1_d38871e1_d38872e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"amz1665702708928__topic_d64142e1_d64143e1_d64144e1_d64145e1_d64146e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d346707e331\">\n                     \n Specialization\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"amz1665702708928__p_d96053e1_d96054e1_d96055e1\">Global ProcScripts are linked into components at runtime.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"amz1665702708928__p_d96056e1_d96057e1_d96058e1\">Global ProcScript specializes Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38873e1_d38874e1_d38875e1\">It has a Global ProcScript Library as parent\n               object. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"amz1665702708928__li_d38876e1_d38877e1_d38878e1\">It has no child objects. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vup1665702853446.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Global ProcScripts</a><p>Global ProcScripts are global objects that are located in a runtime library and can be called from any ProcScript in the application. They enable you to define common functionality for use by one or more applications.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bka1665702579213.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>call</a><p>Execute the specified function or global ProcScript.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3611936\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Global ProcScript Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Global ProcScript A Global ProcScript is a Development Object that defines a ProcScript function that is linked into components at runtime when called by ProcScript in the component. For more information, see Global ProcScripts . Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: prc Main Development Object? No Part of: Global ProcScript Library Contains: Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: ProcName @ LibraryName .prc URI format: libprc: LibraryName /prc: ProcScriptName Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Specialization Global ProcScripts are linked into components at runtime. Global ProcScript specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has a Global ProcScript Library as parent object. It has no child objects. Related Links Global ProcScripts Global ProcScripts are global objects that are located in a runtime library and can be called from any ProcScript in the application. They enable you to define common functionality for use by one or more applications. call Execute the specified function or global ProcScript. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}